token_lists.title: Pareidolia Collection
token_lists.description:
Pareidolia is the psychological phenomenon through which a random stimulus is perceived as significant, and by which we give sense to the reality that surrounds us.

Project Pareidolia aims at collecting humanoid natural formations found on my wanderings through the years.

token_lists.title: Unusual places in the Universe
token_lists.description: There are many unusual cities, landscapes, and planets in parallel worlds of the universe. We cannot visit them in real life. But no one stops us from traveling in our fantasy world.

token_lists.title: Green Macro Sanctuaries
token_lists.description: A collection of macro photography that aims to raise awareness on the importance of caring for nature, the images invite the viewer to appreciate in full detail all the natural beauty that surrounds us every day, and in turn to consciously connect with their own environment in order to take care of it properly.

token_lists.title: Unforeseen Expressions
token_lists.description: Experimentations with photography, pixel sorting code and a vast variety of weird software done by yours truly, A non-coder photographer obsessed with generative arts and CC0 licenses.

token_lists.title: CSRSNT-DAAI Series 6 of 8
token_lists.description: CSRSNT-DAAI is a series of 128 unique 1/1 works. Each of these works is a set of four related images that can be viewed with a custom image viewer.
